1. Authorization by valid username / password
Open the resource https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/ in a browser;
Insert a valid username into the 'Username' field (auto);
Enter a valid password in the 'Password' field (123456qwerty);
Click the "Sign In" button;
Expected Result: Authorization was successful and the 'Sign Out' button is displayed

2. Authorization by invalid username / password
Open the resource https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/ in a browser;
Insert invalid username in the 'Username' field (Aut0);
Enter an invalid password in the 'Password' field (123456QWERTY);
Click the "Sign In" button;
Expected Result: Authorization failed, 'Sign Out' button not displayed

